        "overview_item_data_items": [
          "Reflections change the orientation of the vertices of a figure.",
          "Rigid motions produce congruent figures.",
          "Congruent line segments have the same length.",
          "Congruent angles have equal measures.",
          "You can map congruent figures from one to another through a sequence of translations, reflections, and rotations.",
